This directory holds cross-compiled mar-runtime stubs.

It's populated by `make stubs` (see top-level Makefile). At a fresh
checkout the directory contains only this README so go:embed has at
least one file to match — `go build ./cmd/mar` succeeds but `mar build`
will report missing stubs until `make stubs` runs.

Files added here:
  darwin-amd64     macOS Intel
  darwin-arm64     macOS Apple Silicon
  linux-amd64      Linux x86_64
  linux-arm64      Linux ARM64
  windows-amd64.exe   Windows x86_64

These are large binaries and are not committed to git.
